{"tid":2232582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Apple官方承認 iOS14.0.1 有7大bug！","createTime":"2020-10-06T13:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T13:16:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46f2e80264b1ad2de4cd250d09bc07c1322fb54b","tid":2232582,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nApple 官方承認 iOS 14、WatchOS 7 存在 7 大問題<br />\n連日來本地及外地 iPhone 用家都在網上 Twitter 以及 LIHKG 論壇上表示在使用 iOS 14 系統時出現不同問題，而最多人談論的，應該就是耗電增加，有人的 iPhone 甚至在一個小時內電量由 90％ 跌至 3％<br />\n<br />\n而雖然在 iOS 14 上線數日後，Apple 就已經推出更新的系統版本 iOS 14.0.1，然而這些問題並未得到解決，連 Apple 官方也要發出聲明，指出升級至 iOS 14 或 14.0.1 之後有可能出現的 7 大問題，各位可以留意一下，如果「徵狀」吻合，起碼可以排除是硬件問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201005/389832147512463360.jpeg/RnFE6CN_SLUVZqiJ6HKjhtznHBzUnpBVb6M6Lm-jOi4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201005%2F389832147512463360.jpeg%2FRnFE6CN_SLUVZqiJ6HKjhtznHBzUnpBVb6M6Lm-jOi4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2161e4df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AF%A6%E7%94%A8%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8/531833/apple%E8%AA%8Dios14%E6%9C%897%E5%A4%A7bug-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E9%AC%A7%E7%88%86iphone%E9%9B%BB%E9%87%8F%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C-%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E6%98%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%2F531833%2Fapple%25E8%25AA%2